    dc:description "Figs 1–3. 1–2 – Coptocephala aeneopicta (Fairmaire, 1864): 1 – aedeagus (dorsal, lateral and ventral views); 2 – spermatheca. 3 – aedeagus of Coptocephala arcasi Báguena, 1960 (dorsal, lateral and ventral views). Scale bars: 0.5 mm for Figs 1 and 3, 0.25 mm for Fig. 2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4272773/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

